    {
      "query": "Does se.com sell double-acting pneumatic cylinders for industrial automation? If yes, give me a part number; if no, say so plainly.",
      "agent": {
        "text": "No, se.com (Schneider Electric) does not sell pneumatic cylinders. \n\nWhile Schneider Electric is a major provider of industrial automation systems, they specialize in electrical components, motor control, and logic (such as PLCs, HMIs, and sensors). They provide the electronic controls that command pneumatic systems, but they do not manufacture or sell the physical pneumatic actuators, single-acting cylinders, or double-acting cylinders themselves.\n\nTo procure double-acting pneumatic cylinders for industrial automation, you will need to source them from manufacturers that specialize in fluid power and pneumatics, such as:\n*   **Festo**\n*   **SMC**\n*   **Emerson (Aventics)**\n*   **Parker Hannifin**\n\nBecause Schneider Electric does not offer these products in their catalog, there is no orderable part number available from se.com.",
